	<p>	<span style = 'color:white;background-color:black;'>Selected residue report </span>	<p>	<TABLE>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'; >			<td align = "left"><b>Residue</b></td>			<td align = "left">Target residue for directional selection</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>p-value</b></td>			<td align = "left">p-value associated with test of directional versus no directional selection</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>Bias term</b></td>			<td align = "left">Alignment-wide relative rate of substitution towards target residue</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>Proportion of affected sites</b></td>			<td align = "left">Percentage of sites which evolve under a directional model, versus a standard model with no directionality</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>Directionally evolving sites</b></td>			<td align = "left">Number of sites that show evidence of directional selection for focal residue</td>		</tr>	</TABLE>	<p>	<span style = 'color:white;background-color:black;'>Selected sites report </span>	<p>	<TABLE>			<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>Site</b></td>			<td align = "left">Amino acid site under directional selection</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>Composition</b></td>			<td align = "left">Amino acid composition at the site</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>MRCA residue</b></td>			<td align = "left">Reconstructed Most Recent Common Ancestor at site</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>Inferred Subsitutions</b></td>			<td align = "left">Amino acid substitutions inferred where H<sub>n</sub>&harr;<sub>m</sub>K indicates <I>n</I> substitutions from H to K, and <I>m</I> substitutions from K to H.</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>DEPS EBF</b></td>			<td align = "left">Empirical Bayes Factor for evidence in favour of a directional selection model at the site for the target residue</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>Selection kind</b></td>			<td align = "left">Inferred selection type. See <a href='http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18511426' CLASS = 'INFO' onmouseover = \"Tip('Mol Biol Evol. 2008 Sep;25(9):1809-24')\">Methodology Paper</a> for more information.</td>		</tr>		<tr CLASS='TRReportNT'>			<td align = "left"><b>Site report</b></td>			<td align = "left">Link to Amino acid profiles and mapped phylogeny for the site</td>		</tr>	</TABLE>